{"tid":2303891,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中環歷山大廈米芝蓮3星意大利餐廳「8 1/2 Otto e Mezzo BOMBANA」有1名廚師確診","createTime":"2020-11-28T10:10:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T10:10:05.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"88982a9fedfd95b8248007febaf850167d34e9bd","tid":2303891,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T10:10:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/4XAicPIGk.JWJ.ZCXrQ3KA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NS41Mzg0NjE1Mzg0NjE1/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/UCTbq525RlShaFAJVt6GMA--~B/aD01NTc7dz03ODA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/onccinstantnews.com/e71e4d0be2843750c49c1764ec351b70\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F4XAicPIGk.JWJ.ZCXrQ3KA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NS41Mzg0NjE1Mzg0NjE1%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FUCTbq525RlShaFAJVt6GMA--~B%2FaD01NTc7dz03ODA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2Fe71e4d0be2843750c49c1764ec351b70&h=9abd2db2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n肺炎疫情愈爆愈多，確診者更涉及本地知名食店。衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君今(28日)公布，位於中環歷山大廈的米芝蓮3星意大利餐廳「8 1/2 Otto e Mezzo BOMBANA」有1名廚師確診、同店1名侍應亦初步確診。衞生防護中心已要求該餐廳停業，其他員工亦要入住檢疫中心。<br />\n<br />\n根據資料顯示，該餐廳於2011年獲得米芝蓮「2星」殊榮，由2012年起至今，更被米芝蓮升格至「3星」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/HUL0cGyFS0bVw9fD3BN.6w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/onccinstantnews.com/7de8b7b0b8272fecb3ee644ebb0fce1d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FHUL0cGyFS0bVw9fD3BN.6w--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F7de8b7b0b8272fecb3ee644ebb0fce1d&h=466a8667&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/中環意大利米芝蓮餐廳2員工染疫-其餘職員須隔離檢疫-085024350.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E4%B8%AD%E7%92%B0%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9%E7%B1%B3%E8%8A%9D%E8%93%AE%E9%A4%90%E5%BB%B32%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E6%9F%93%E7%96%AB-%E5%85%B6%E9%A4%98%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E9%A0%88%E9%9A%94%E9%9B%A2%E6%AA%A2%E7%96%AB-085024350.html&d=xEw7bVcEuEkne8wYN5Y7CiNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=980a153e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/中環意大利米芝蓮餐廳2員工染疫-其餘職員須隔離檢疫-085024350.html</a>"}]}